  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de Phonon</title>

    <para>Make sure that <xref linkend="qt4"/> is compiled without the bundled
    <application>Phonon</application> library. Ce paquet fournit
    a better implementation.</para>
    
    <para>Installez <application>Phonon</application> en lançant les commandes
    suivantes&nbsp;:</para>>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build</userinput></screen>

    <para>Préparation du paquet pour la compilation:</para>
       
<screen><userinput>cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=$QT4DIR \
      .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>&nbsp;:</para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

